      <title>利雅得捍卫欧佩克+减产后，石油开始复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯表示，欧佩克+最近的减产将得到全面落实，并且可能会延长，这打消了人们对限制措施有效性的怀疑，油价止住了连续下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-5</guid>
